[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0258","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0115","title":"IBM AIX bugfiler 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 3.x 操作系统中的 bugfiler 程序存在任意文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者利用该程序可创建或覆盖系统文件，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 AIX 3.x 版本，攻击者仅需本地账户即可利用，无需用户交互，危害较高，CVSS 评分 7.2。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0115"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.230","remediation":"升级 AIX 系统至 4.1.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续发行版中修复。临时缓解措施：以 root 执行 `chmod u-s /usr/bin/bugfiler` 移除 setuid 特权位，防止本地用户通过 bugfiler 获取 root Shell；若无需使用 bugfiler 工具，可直接 `chmod 700 /usr/bin/bugfiler` 限制仅 root 可执行。请评估是否需同时更新 `bos.rte.security` 文件集的相关安全补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1800","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20290","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0115","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0115.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pf77-c4gh-6m4v/GHSA-pf77-c4gh-6m4v.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0115.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0258.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0257","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0257.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0114","title":"Elm elm-2.4 邮件系统本地符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Elm-2.4 邮件客户端中的 filter 命令存在符号链接（symlink）攻击漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在临时目录中创建恶意符号链接，诱使 filter 命令以其他用户的权限执行任意命令或读取敏感文件。该漏洞利用条件为拥有本地账户权限，影响范围包括使用 Elm-2.4 的 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。建议升级到不受影响的版本或禁用 filter 功能。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0114"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.097","remediation":"立即升级至 Elm 2.4 Patch Level 3 及以上版本，该版本修复了 filter 命令在处理临时文件时的竞态条件问题。若无法升级，建议禁用 filter 命令或移除 elm 的 setuid 权限位以限制 symlink 攻击。长期建议迁移至 mutt 或 alpine 等持续维护的邮件客户端。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0114"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0257.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0256","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0256.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0113","title":"IBM AIX rlogin 权限提升漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 3.2.5 的 rlogin 实现中存在参数注入漏洞（CWE-88），当向 rlogin 命令传入 `-froot` 参数时，未经授权的本地攻击者可利用该参数绕过正常的身份认证机制，以 root 权限直接登录目标系统，实现权限提升。该漏洞源于程序未对命令行参数进行有效过滤和消毒，攻击者无需知道目标用户密码即可获取系统最高控制权。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 3.2.5 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0113"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1994-05-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.820","remediation":"建议立即升级 IBM AIX 至 4.1.0 及以上版本（该漏洞已在 AIX 4.x 中修复），或安装对应 APAR 补丁。同时禁用 rlogin/rsh/r-commands 系列服务（注释 /etc/inetd.conf 中相关行并重启 inetd），迁移至 OpenSSH 替代远程管理。限制 root 远程登录，在 /etc/securetty 中移除不必要的终端，并启用 PAM 认证机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/458","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19348","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0113","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0113.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0113.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/604.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/rlogin_froot.nasl","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/609.txt","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/murahari1/recon-tool/blob/f63a205225373d0d87b081758c11899777970b0f/README.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0256.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0255","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0255.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0691","title":"多款 Unix 系统 CDE dtaction 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CDE 桌面环境 dtaction 工具中的 AddSuLog 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该函数传递超长的用户名字符串参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而获取目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞影响 DIGITAL UNIX 4.0、AIX 4.3.2、IRIX 6.5.14、Solaris 7.0 等多个 Unix 操作系统上的 CDE 2.1 版本，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需具有本地系统账号方能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0691"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.420","remediation":"对于 Solaris 7.0，安装 Sun Security Bulletin #192 提供的补丁；AIX 4.3.2 安装 IBM APAR IY07482 补丁；HP-UX 应用 HPSBUX9909-103 公告补丁；Digital UNIX 4.0 安装 Compaq SSRT0746U 补丁；IRIX 6.5.14 安装 SGI 19990901-01-P 补丁。临措：移除 dtaction 的 setuid 位，`chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtaction`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/635","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A3078","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19497","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0691.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0691.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0691","https://github.com/0xMarcio/cve/blob/a60c64eb75d37dbb82a1f2a085e4be6cfbbc462e/1999/CVE-1999-0691.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rq63-6647-rqxc/GHSA-rq63-6647-rqxc.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/ff974b2b48bc0a9f1df6a8c109ec03abf4db2138/1999/CVE-1999-0691.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0255.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0254","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0690","title":"HP CDE 将当前目录加入 root 的 PATH 环境变量导致权限提升漏洞","description":"HP CDE（Common Desktop Environment）在设置 root 用户环境变量 PATH 时错误地将当前目录 \".\" 包含在内，导致本地攻击者可在任意目录中放置与系统命令同名的恶意程序，当 root 用户通过 su 或登录进入该目录并执行未指定路径的命令时，恶意程序将以 root 权限自动执行，实现本地提权。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 系统中运行 CDE 的版本，需要攻击者拥有本地 shell 访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0690"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.300","remediation":"编辑 root 用户的 .profile、.login 或 CDE 系统级配置文件 /etc/dt/config/Xsession.d/ 下的相关脚本，移除 PATH 中的当前目录（即删除 \".\" 或空路径项），确保 PATH 仅包含绝对路径的系统目录（如 /usr/bin:/usr/sbin）。同时建议修改 CDE 启动脚本中 PATH 的拼接方式，使用完整路径调用命令，消除当前目录隐式搜索带来的提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-053.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-100","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0690","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0690.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx/GHSA-rf75-mr45-vgcx.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cwe_details/cwe_details_300_400.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0690.json","https://github.com/Team-Atlanta/aixcc-asc-atlantis/blob/785c446f980e12155935db586aa30c3b54adcc86/crs/src/crs-patch/smith/smith/lib/cwe/raw/CWE-427.txt","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/CWE-Expert/blob/f634e911e6c24a1ad8b9619383e2ab3eb2d9ebd4/CWE_corpus/markdown/4_cwe_trimmed_top25.md.txt","https://github.com/ws-researcher/CAEA/blob/098ddb07c83845feda3d1b1d56ef634927954af4/KGA/dataSet/ICNS/entN_ids_1"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0254.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0253","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0253.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0112","title":"IBM AIX CDE dtterm 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 4.2 系统中的 CDE 桌面环境 dtterm 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。未授权本地攻击者可通过向 dtterm 程序传递特制的超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖函数返回地址，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞要求攻击者拥有系统本地账号，影响 AIX 4.2 版本及可能更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0112"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.680","remediation":"建议升级至 AIX 4.3 及以上版本，或安装 IBM 提供的相应 APAR 补丁。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/dt/bin/dtterm 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtterm），并限制可执行该程序的用户组，仅授权可信用户访问 CDE 环境。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/878","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/333","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0112","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0112.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0112.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3xqj-xx96-hm93/GHSA-3xqj-xx96-hm93.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83084/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0112.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0253.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0252","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0252.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0111","title":"IBM AIX RIP v1 路由欺骗漏洞","description":"RIP v1 是一种距离向量路由协议，其设计缺陷在于未对路由更新报文进行身份认证，导致攻击者可通过伪造 RIP 广播报文向目标系统注入虚假路由条目。AIX 系统上运行的 RIP v1 服务存在欺骗漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可在同一广播域内发送精心构造的 RIP 响应报文，篡改目标主机的路由表，将流量重定向至攻击者控制的恶意节点，进而实现中间人攻击、信息窃取或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 AIX 系统上启用了 RIP v1 服务的配置，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0111"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.543","remediation":"建议升级支持 RIPv2 的路由软件以启用 MD5 认证，或迁移至 OSPF 等认证型路由协议；在边界路由器上配置被动接口并实施 RIP 路由过滤（distribute-list），仅允许与已知邻居通信，阻断伪造 RIP 路由更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0111"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0252.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0251","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0251.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0110","title":"Sun Solaris fdformat 命令缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"CVE-1999-0110 已被 CVE 组织废弃，该编号是 CVE-1999-0315 的重复项，因原始描述中的拼写错误导致未能及时识别为重复记录。实际对应漏洞为：Sun Solaris 系统中 fdformat 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该命令传递特制输入参数触发溢出，覆盖内存数据并执行任意代码，从而获取 root 权限。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限方可利用，影响 Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1/7.0 等版本，CVSS v2 评分为 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0110"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2023-11-07T01:54:55.093","remediation":"安装 Sun 安全公告 #138 提供的对应 Solaris 版本补丁：Solaris 2.3/2.4/2.5/2.5.1/7.0 分别有对应补丁包。如系统已停止官方支持，建议升级至 Solaris 10 或更新版本。临时缓解措施：限制不可信本地用户登录系统，移除 fdformat 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/fdformat）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0251.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0250","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0250.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0109","title":"Sun Solaris ffbconfig 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.5.1 的 ffbconfig 图形配置工具存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 ffbconfig 程序传递特制参数触发缓冲区溢出，覆盖进程内存空间，从而获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.5.1 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需要拥有本地系统账号才能利用此漏洞实施提权攻击。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0109"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.407","remediation":"立即应用 Sun Security Bulletin #140 提供的补丁程序，或直接升级到 Solaris 7 及以上版本。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/sbin/ffbconfig 的 setuid 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/ffbconfig），限制本地非授权用户执行该命令，防止普通用户利用缓冲区溢出提权至 root。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/140","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19159","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0109","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0109.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7xv-wfqv-x2wf/GHSA-m7xv-wfqv-x2wf.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0109.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154300_154400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0250.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0249","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0249.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0689","title":"Sun Solaris Common Desktop Environment dtspcd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Common Desktop Environment (CDE) 的 dtspcd 守护进程存在符号链接（symlink）漏洞，本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接诱导 dtspcd 以提升的权限读取或写入任意文件，从而执行任意命令获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 CDE 2.1.20 及 Solaris 7.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0689"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.173","remediation":"安装 Sun 安全公告 #192 中对应平台的 dtspcd 补丁（Solaris 7：Patch ID 106594-01；Solaris 2.6：106593-01；Solaris 2.5.1：106592-01），HP-UX 用户安装 HPSBUX9909-103 补丁。临时缓解措施可停止 dtspcd 服务（/usr/dt/bin/dtspcd -kill）或移除其 setuid root 权限（chmod 555 /usr/dt/bin/dtspcd）。由于 CDE 已停止维护，建议迁移至 GNOME/KDE 等其他桌面环境作为根本解决方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/636","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1880","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19498","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0689.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0689","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0689.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0689.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wp6j-p4jf-4rwv/GHSA-wp6j-p4jf-4rwv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c3dc2ea0-0265-4c0c-ae08-6be3c238c97a.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0689.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0249.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0249.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0249.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0248","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0688","title":"HP 软件分发器 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"HP-UX 系统的软件分发器（Software Distributor，简称 SD）在 10.x 与 11.x 版本中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞源于 SD 组件在处理特定输入时未对数据长度做充分边界校验，导致攻击者可控的过长数据写入固定大小的缓冲区，进而可覆盖相邻内存并可能实现任意代码执行。影响范围为运行 HPUX 10.x 和 11.x 且启用 SD 服务的系统。攻击条件为攻击者需能够向目标系统的 SD 服务发送特制请求，通常需要一定的本地或相邻网络访问权限。利用方式为构造恶意输入触发缓冲区溢出，造成服务异常或提升权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0688"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.047","remediation":"立即安装 HP-UX 11.11 或更高版本的 HP Software Distributor 补丁 HPD4365-11，或者应用 HPSBUX9907-101 安全更新。如需继续使用 HPUX 10.x，请应用 HP SD 10.20 补丁套件。立即更新系统，关闭不必要的 SD 服务以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/545","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9907-101","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0688","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0688.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r/GHSA-873q-3c4x-555r.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0688.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--9b15c9ce-60ad-4d9f-bb76-76ab2ab118a8.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0248.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0247","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0247.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0108","title":"SGI IRIX 6.3 xrm 本地缓冲区溢出权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 6.3 操作系统的 printers 程序中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xrm 组件提交特制的输入数据触发缓冲区溢出，导致以 root 权限执行任意代码，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞仅需本地用户权限即可利用，影响 SGI IRIX 6.3 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0108"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.280","remediation":"升级 SGI IRIX 至 6.4 及以上版本，或安装 SGI 提供的补丁程序。作为临时缓解措施，限制对受影响系统的本地访问权限，仅授权可信用户使用，并移除 setuid 权限位。鉴于 IRIX 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://seclists.org/bugtraq/1997/May/191","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19267","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0108","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0108.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0108.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5